# State Management Diagram

## ROGUE NEURAL - State Management Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[useGameLogic Hook] --> B[GameState Context]
    A --> C[Scenario State]
    A --> D[UI State]
    A --> E[Game Logic State]

    B --> B1[loading]
    B --> B2[scenario]
    B --> B3[playing]
    B --> B4[ended]

    C --> C1[Current Scenario]
    C --> C2[Scenario History]
    C --> C3[Entity States]

    D --> D1[Loading Screen]
    D --> D2[Scenario Display]
    D --> D3[Game Interface]

    E --> E1[Chaos Level]
    E --> E2[Current Phase]
    E --> E3[Phase History]
    E --> E4[Logs]

    A --> F[Action Dispatchers]
    F --> F1[startGame]
    F --> F2[handleChoice]
    F --> F3[resetGame]
    F --> F4[nextPhase]

    F --> B
    F --> C
    F --> D
    F --> E

    B --> G[Component Rendering]
    C --> G
    D --> G
    E --> G

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style B fill:#fff3e0
    style C fill:#f3e5f5
    style D fill:#e8f5e9
    style E fill:#fce4ec
```

