## ROGUE NEURAL - State Transition Flow

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initial

    Initial: Initializing
    Initial --> Loaded: On Mount

    Loaded: Waiting for User
    Loaded --> Loading: startGame()

    Loading: Loading Scenario
    Loading --> ScenarioReady: Data Loaded

    ScenarioReady: Displaying Scenario
    ScenarioReady --> Playing: Start Game

    Playing: Active Gameplay
    Playing --> ProcessingChoice: Choice Selected

    ProcessingChoice: Evaluating Choice
    ProcessingChoice --> InPhase: Validation Passed
    ProcessingChoice --> ScenarioReady: Error

    InPhase: Displaying Phase
    InPhase --> ProcessingChoice: Next Choice
    InPhase --> PhaseComplete: Phase Done

    PhaseComplete: Next Phase Setup
    PhaseComplete --> InPhase: More Phases
    PhaseComplete --> CalculatingEnding: Last Phase

    CalculatingEnding: Determine Ending
    CalculatingEnding --> EndingExploding: Chaos > 80
    CalculatingEnding --> EndingHackerman: Chaos < 20
    CalculatingEnding --> EndingBetrayal: Chaos 20-80

    EndingExploding: Explosive Ending
    EndingHackerman: Hackerman Ending
    EndingBetrayal: Betrayal Ending

    EndingExploding --> GameOver: End Animation
    EndingHackerman --> GameOver
    EndingBetrayal --> GameOver

    GameOver: Final State
    GameOver --> Loaded: Reset Game
    GameOver --> [*]

    style Initial fill:#e0e0e0
    style Playing fill:#b3e5fc
    style GameOver fill:#ffcdd2
```

